      <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
      <p>Barber Stewart McVittie & Wallace Insurance Brokers has been part of the Canadian insurance landscape since 1880 — making us one of the longest-standing brokerages in the country.</p>
      <p>Over the decades, the brokerage grew through a series of mergers and acquisitions. In 1967 it became Barber Stewart Limited, in 1968 it merged with Henry McWilliams and Wallace Limited, and in 1975 the merger with the R.D. McVittie Agency gave us the name we carry today.</p>
      <p>In 2013, under new ownership, BSMW began a new chapter — blending its deep industry expertise with modern technology. In 2015, we expanded to Eastern Ontario and opened our Kingston location to better serve clients in the region.</p>
      <p>Today, BSMW partners with top North American insurers including Aviva, RSA, Chubb, Travelers, Economical, Unica, and Lloyd's to deliver coverage built around each client's real needs.</p>
